<div style="text-align: center;"><big>Here is a list of articles that need to be cleaned up. A list of these pages ordered by importance/popularity can be obtained using WMFLabs' MassViews tool here: [https://tools.wmflabs.org/massviews/?platform=all-access&agent=user&source=category&target=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3AAll_pages_needing_cleanup&range=last-week&subjectpage=1&subcategories=1&sort=views&direction=1&view=list MassViews Analysis] (Takes a couple minutes to load due to the size of the list) Pick one and do your best. {{Random page in category}}</big></div>
<categorytree>All pages needing cleanup</categorytree>
{{Filter category by topic}}

